Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,20,,Have you heard the gossip already?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,20,,And have you made sure yourself with those eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,20,,Two shockingly beautiful glazzies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,20,,A shockingly overflowing romance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,20,,The hottest topic now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,20,,It's all about this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,20,,A charming lady from the Taishou Era
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,20,,Here she is, High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,20,,Here she is, High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,20,,Here she is, High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,20,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The ways of God are strange and chose this fiancé for Benio,{何の因果か紅緒にとって信じられないこの人が}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving her utterly baffled.{親の決めたる言いなずけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, all of a sudden,{突如襲った荒くれ者を}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,some bad guys try to beat her up,{腹立ちまぎれにお相手すれば}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.21,0:01:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but a mysterious woman saves her:{冥界ちり}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,she's a geisha in love with Shinobu.{これまたshouiに片思い}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocked, Benio thinks Shinobu is a playboy.{ショックは歴然shouiはプレイボーイなり}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the final straw that makes Benio decide to go home once and for all,{ここは年貢の納め時おんでる決心したところ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but a sudden letter by Nanny hinders again,{帰ってくるなとこれは懐かしいばあやのたより}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,our poor High Collar Lady can't decide what to do!{はてさてままにならないはいからさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please treat the objects with care.{さあ丁寧に扱うのですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll carry them to the second floor's balcony in a sunlit spot.{日当たりのいい2階のバルコニーに運ぶんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I place this?{グレーどこに置きましょうか}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you can place it there.{その辺に置いてちょうだい}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you airing objects, ma'am?{虫干しですかおばあ様}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This mansion is rather old, so there's a lot to do.{これだけ古い家だからたくさんあるでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be tough! Then, I'll try to help too!{大変ですねそれじゃあ私も手伝います}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!{やめて}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, you can leave it there,{Benioさんはよろしいのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,no need to strain yourself.{何時もせずっともう}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:42.37,Sign,,0,0,0,,well{with displeasure}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:42.37,Sign,,0,0,0,,ha{/ho-ho}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like you don't trust me...{なんか信用ないのだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,200)\c&HE2DDDD&\pos(467.027,146.667)\bord0\blur0.667\fs60\b1}Episode 15\NSo long, old-fashioned mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that long face?{どうしたの浮かない顔しちゃって}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling left out in this airing.{私は仲間外れなのよむしぼしの}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, aren't you happy that you can slack off?{あら結構じゃないのサボれて}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true,{それはそうだけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd like some company.{でも付き合ってもがあるでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about airing some of your belongings?{だったらbenioさんの身の回りのものでも虫干ししたらどう}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think I have anything antiquated enough...{でも私には虫干しするような古臭い品物なんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's one!{あったわ一つだけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It symbolises the vow that a woman makes not to marry a second time ever.{\i0}{白い喪服は二府にまみえずという女の証なのだよ - ep 6, 4:19 for reference}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In case something happens to him{もしもしの?にまいちのことがあった時}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to wear this.{これを使いなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so old fashioned, Father...{古臭いんだなお父様も}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't remaining faitfhul to your husband{妻が夫にずんずるかいなかわ(?)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,be determined by the couple's love?{二人の愛情で決まることじゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a dagger.{かいけんだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens to Shinobu,{shouiにまいちなことがあったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I should die by using this...{これで死ねっていうの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, how do you feel about me?{SHOUI,あなた私のことどう思っているの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Our moments together should give you the answer.{過ぎ去りし日々が何かを語りかけているはず}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Our moments together...{過ぎ去りし日々}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaves are falling, but it's not Autumn yet...{秋でもないのにこの葉が1枚あ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to go away! I t-{来ないでったら、こ--}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:04:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,let's flee, quick!{早く逃げるんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?{なんだなんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My heartbeat...{この胸のときめきが}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I happen to be in...{この吉次はね伊集院の若様に}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,love with Young Master.{惚れておりましたのさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't Shinobu?{私の少尉じゃなかったんだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, did you meet her?{benioさん彼女に会ったんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to respect him.{少尉も?まみえず- idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My love has finally come true!{私の恋がついに\N結ばれる日が来たのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I beg you not to ever come back home.{\i0}{お願いですから何があっても家だけには戻らないでください}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, did you meet her?{benioさん彼女に会ったんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't ever come back...{\i0}{決して戻らないで。。。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll have to respect him.{\i0}{少尉も?まみえず- idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My love...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I ever die for someone{愛情がはっきりしない人のためになって}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that can't express his feelings!?{死なるわけないじゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate this! I hate this so much!{ああ嫌よ、こんなの嫌よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, what's wrong?{Benio様とっとと}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop it, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what it looks like!{誤解よー}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait, I said!{待って、待ってったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! There's been a misunderstanding!{待って、違うよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, for God's sake!{落ち着いてよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only be calm when I'm safe!{/saved/helped}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait, Mrs. Kisaragi!{待ってよ如月さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi, hang in there!{きさらぎさんしっかりして}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, hang in there, Mrs. Kisaragi!{しっかりしてきさらぎさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how silly of me!{私としたことが}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-oh-oh! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You got rid of this hag in the blink of an eye! Congratulations!{ついにそのババをバラす化身が付き合いしたかこいつをめでとう}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this nonsense you're saying?{何を馬鹿なこと言ってんの}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, hurry up and lend me a hand!{ushigorou早く手を貸して}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You even know resuscitation!{喝を入れられるなんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, you truly are something else!{親分大したもんでござんすねぇ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ah, I have a full mastership, after all!{これでも私は諸岡という免許皆伝}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Mrs. Kisaragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This sword is surely very refined, as expected!{さすが小松五郎をよしこにの期待しわざわの\N役切れたのー I don't understand clearly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,During the battle of Toba-Fushimi{すぐる鳥羽伏見の戦いでは}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so young...{わしも若かった}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,En garde! Get ready to die!{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, it's enough...{もうやめ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi, hang in there, please!{kisaragiさんしっかりしてねしっかりして}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what should I do?{アリアンどうしよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Count, let's call a doctor,{おじい様お医者様を呼びましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't handle this by ourselves.{私たちの手には負えません}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can call.{まあ、呼ぶんがいい}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, call Dr. Yamada.{うしごろう、やまだはかせを呼んで}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call Yamada!{山田はいかん}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so?{なぜです}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He lives up and right from here.{博士の家はここから東北}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the North-East.{すなわち丑寅の方位にあった}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And North-East is an unpropitious direction.{本日の暗剣殺は丑寅なのじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling a doctor from an unfavourable direction{暗剣殺の方角から医者を呼ぶと}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,would bring no good!{助かるものも助からん}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this fiction?{何を演技担いでるんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fiction, it's faith!{演技ではない信念じゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just a superstition!{いいえ信念ではなくて 迷信です}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking by experience!{わしは経験にもとせもの言う通るんじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the 3rd of January at the beginning of the Meiji era,{時は明治元年1月3日}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,during the battle of Toba-Fushimi.{鳥羽伏見の戦いにおいて}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guided the Satsuma battalion,{わしは薩摩隼人の一体を引き連れて}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and near Fushimi, I saw something.{伏見のあたりをしておった}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I could distinctly recognise the enemies from a distance.{この時前方の敵が\N暗剣殺の方向にいる方は知った}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I realised that that direction would've been unfavourable for us,{暗剣殺に向かっていくとはに赴くまともじゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so I started to plan.{そこでワシワだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We turned around,{暗剣殺を打ち消す剣道の方向から}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we waded across the river{わざわざを返して}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and we walked into the enemy's territory!{とっとと敵陣に攻め入ったり}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!{つっこめ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed to sweep through that battle with no casualties.{核って言わなくんは一平も損なわず爆群は\N飛ばした}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this was because we avoided an unfavourable direction!{これすなわち暗剣殺を避けたればこそじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just a coincidence!{そんなのは偶然です}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you planning to say those antiquated things?{いつまでそんな古臭いこと言ってるんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You old timer!{この時代遅れ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's an old timer!?{次回遅れとはなんじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that your mentality is old!{遅れているんですよその頭が}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Grr...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaddup, you tomboy!{黙れこのおてんば}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You blockhead!{このわからず屋}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You obstinate hoyden!{このじゃじゃうま娘}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't understand}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief, they're wasting my time.{全くこの忙しいのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did Kisaragi go?{如月はどこへ行ってしまったのじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Kisaragi?{おい如月はどうした}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so busy and she's nowhere to be seen!{この忙しいのにどこで何をしておる}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could she have gone? It's not like her.{本にどこへ行ったのでしょうあの人らしくもない}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take care then.{はいそれではお大事に}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.{どうもありがとうございました}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake?{気がつきましたか}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a bit of overwork, so if you rest for 23 days you'll be okay.{ただの過労だから23日ゆっくりしてれば治るそうです}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But wasn't Dr. Yamada from North-East?{でも山田博士は丑寅の方角からいらしたん\Nでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I firmly made him come here!{ええ私が断固として来ていただきました}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, that's awful!{丑寅の方が}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{だからもしかすると助かるものも助かりません - Don't know}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding for now!{それは冗談}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mrs. Kisaragi, you're sure old fashioned.{でも如月さんも古いんですね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm fully aware.{えーどうせ私は古い女です}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get up yet.{いけません}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But... resting in a day like this...{でも今日という日に休んでいるわけには}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I've got permission from both Count and Ma'am, so that you can rest with no trouble.{いいえおじいさまとおばあさまが くれぐれも\Nきさらぎさんを休ませておくようきつこう してありましたから}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, thank ya and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that doctor Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell called for that doctor?{誰があの医者を呼んだのじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that I hate those North-East chaps!{あれほど言うたのに安定させる方角から呼ぶと\Nは}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it? Who called the quack?{誰じゃ 誰が呼んだのじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I apologise...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever,{もう良い}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already understood who it was.{聞かずとも大型けんとうとはついた}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:14:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There is just one person that would dare disobeying my orders!{東亜屋敷でわしの言葉に逆らう奴はあいつ\Nしかおらん}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you call the doctor?{なぜ医者を呼んだんじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We needed him so I called him.{はい必要だから呼びました}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you ever listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kisaragi?{如月はどこじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She is resting.{休んでいます}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!? Who authorised her?{何？誰が休暇を赦した?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How come!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I am currently an apprentice bride,{私は花嫁修行中です}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have to learn how to take care of a house myself.{後藤家の使用人は私の監督家にあるんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a problem with that!?{文句あるか}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My loss...{負けそう}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a commemoration from Ise during the Meiji Era.{これは明治さんがお伊勢にあらしゃったおりの御記念 - idk about this one}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite an important piece of history!{ゆいしょのあるものでございますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!{気をつけて}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world could be inside this?{一体何が入ってるのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So this plate is such a precious thing?{こんな皿大事にとっておくほどのものかね}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My cat's is better than this- ah!{うちの猫のサラだってまた綺麗だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, silly me, I broke it!{あらやだ割れちゃった}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!{すいません}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter?{あらどうしたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all serious right now.{みんな深刻な顔しちゃって}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Chill! It's not like I broken the tectonic plate!{平気よお膝の皿が割れたわけじゃなし - originally a joke with hiza no sara, meaning kneecap, I adapted it}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to glue the pieces!{ノリで貼れば元通りよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the airing going?{どうじゃ赤取っとるか}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could my plate be?{わしの皿はどこかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there it is!.{おーあった}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This colour, this gloss, {この色このツヤさすがは島津高校歌手の恋まり}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who broke it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it slipped...{joke is boku is male ver of "me" and watashi is female, ziu knows about that from luminous something-san - pere}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,F-F-F... Fi-fi-fi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fix this immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Death penalty.{死刑}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Death penalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, please wait!{ご前、お待ちくださいませ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You shut up!{いええ、黙っておれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away!{にげるなと}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You cunt!{申すに}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I didn't think his old mentality could reach these levels!{まったくも時代錯誤もここまで来ると残虐ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio! Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Count, please quit it immediately!{じい様いい加減にしてください}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting so furious over a stupid plate...{バカなお皿1枚とお手打ちだなんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A plate versus a human life,\Nwhich one is more important?{お皿と人の命とどっちが大事なんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A plate!{皿じゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well...{負けた}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That plate is no ordinary plate!{この皿はなただの皿ではないのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Shimazu of Satsuma in person handed it down to me,{薩摩の島津候がおん手ずからわしに下賜された}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's a heirloom for my family!{いわば我が家の家宝なのじゃぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Be it ten plates or one plate broken, it would ruin my honour as a samurai!{十枚が一枚かけてもわしの武士としての面目がたたぬわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't back off! My honour as a samurai is on the line!{成敗いたすわしの武士としての誇りにかけて}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,please contain your rage.{お気持ち押し詰めになって}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even If I relax, my plate won't be fixed!{気を静めても皿は元に戻らん}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, but...{それはそうでございますが}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, it could be a cursed plate,{とにかく番町皿屋敷じゃあるまいし - reference to banchou sarayashiki, a folk legend from Japan - here she says "aru mai", which is like "nai", but honestly it doesn't make sense with the following line by Ranmaru}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so I would be cautious...{そんな皿1枚で。。。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I won't die completely and my ghost will haunt you forever!{そうよ私だって死んでも死にきれないわ化けて出ちゃうから}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A fashion plate man, a man-{男一枚よ男。。。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, maid, you won't die alone!{安心せい女中お前一人を死なせません}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?{それどういう意味}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,After killing you, I'll commit suicide to set myself free from this dishonour!{お前を手打ちにしてわしもしわばらかっさばいておわびを}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out the way, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Or won't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tenmaru, Chimaru?{どうした天マルチマル}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anything happen here?{何かあったのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Sublieutenant, just in time!{shouiの旦那いいところ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, what is it?{うしごろどうした}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's terrible!{大変なんですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss and Ranmaru-- err, Ranko, are...{親分とらんまるええええ蘭子が}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru, show us the way!{テンマルチマル案内を頼む}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang! If anything bad happens to Boss,{畜生め親分にまいいちのことがあってみろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:19:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll set this whole mansion on fire!{心地火つけてやるからの}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,get out the way!{そこどけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you deaf!?{耳がないのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear me?{聞こえんのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!{どけという}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...{紅緒さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done, Benio!?{何をするのじゃbenioよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better this way.{これでいいんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you break... my plates!?{なぜ皿をわしの皿を}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me too, I beg you.{私もお手打ちにしてください}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to kill someone for a plate,{皿1枚で人一人を切るのなら}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,if the other nine get broken, you'd have to kill nine people.{残り9枚の皿を割れば\N9人の人が切らなければなりません}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'll take the responsibility for those nine.{その9人分の命を私が引き受けましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, finish me off!{さあどうぞお切りください}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...{benioさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,En garde!{覚悟}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this anymore!{もう我慢できねー}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ushigorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No use in meddling.{手出しは無用}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Boss!{だって親分がよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio will forge her own destiny.{benioさんは自分で運命を切り開く}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!{畜生}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, old hag!{おいババ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You creep! How dare you barge into a woman's room with no permission!?{断りもなしに女性の部屋へこの礼儀知らずが}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:21:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You dumbass! This is not the time to laze off!{xめのんびり寝てる場合じゃねえてんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was given permission by Lord...{でも私は殿様に許されて休暇を}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure don't know anything, ignorance is bliss!{お前さん何も知らねえんだな長生きするぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Boss has taken all the responsibility on herself to allow you to rest!{休暇はな親分が責任を引っかぶってお前さんも休ませてるんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool is going to be murdered in no time!{その親分がよ\N手打ちにされかかってんだぞなんと}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She {\i1}what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You better get ready!{良い覚悟じゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish, I'll murder you!{望み通り刀の錆びついしてくれる}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming{ at you}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:22:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From now on, you'll be part of the Ijuuin family,{\i0}{これからはお前も伊集院家の人間}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}take care of yourself.{\i0}{体には気をつけるのだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...{お父様}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for the sadness that awaits.{先立つ不幸をお許しください}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu is just going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.30,0:22:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,watch me get killed, isn't he?{見殺しするんのね}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't oppose to his scary grandfather.{怖いお爺様に逆らえないのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you!{嫌い}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you!{嫌い}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Count from Satsuma's rage has reached its peak,{薩摩隼人の老伯爵は怒り怒って待ったなし}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and is ready to murder the young Hanamura Benio,{俗妙hanamura benioとうめんとって17歳}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,who has had enough of Shinobu's lack of resoluteness!{役に立たない腰抜けshouiを恨んであの嫁なく\Nが良い}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.23,0:22:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, the only person she can count on, is just standing there, dumbfounded.{唯一の便りのShouiはただ茫然と立ちんぼう}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, our High Collar Lady has already made up her mind,{さればもはやこれまでと覚悟を決めたはいからさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, how sad it is for a youthful seventeen year-old girl to die like this...{あー哀れ花の命は短くて17歳の若き紅緒もこれまでか}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The faint and fleeting contact with Shinobu,{shouiとの淡く儚き触れ合いも - I didn't understand this one}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is it just a vanishing dream or an illusion?{消えゆく夢かまぼろしか}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Here Comes the Smart Alec:\NFarewell, failed bride{いざさらば落第花嫁}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,7,,How are you feeling? I'm Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.36,Default,,0,0,7,,Please call me a High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that period
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,7,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,7,,I just want to know what's in his heart, \Nwhile he goes away{added} I want him to turn around,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,7,,to give me once again this loving glance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,7,,Ah, how frustrating it is for me \Nto have this unrequited feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,7,,How are you feeling? I'm Benio
